in accordance with applicable federal state and local laws energy xxi complies with applicable state and local laws governing nondiscrimination in employment in every location in which the company has facilities this policy applies to all terms and conditions of employment including but not limited to hiring placement promotion termination layoff recall transfer leaves of absence compensation and training energy xxi expressly prohibits any form of unlawful employee harassment based on race color religion gender sexual orientation gender identity or expression national origin age genetic information disability or veteran status improper interference with the ability of energy xxi employees to perform their expected job duties is absolutely not tolerated about energy xxi community outreach our operations operation overview main pass complex west delta ship shoal grand isle south timbalier onshore tariffs investor relations press releases sec filings events  presentations email alerts faqs ir contact leadership board of directors management team corporate governance careers our culture  overview benefits job search stay current sign up to receive uptodate news about energy xxi in the news recent releases   contact energy xxi  main suite  houston  texas  t  f  investor relations media relations rss subscribe   energy xxi      privacy statement      terms of use operation overview  energy xxi about energy xxi community outreach our operations operation overview main pass complex west delta ship shoal grand isle south timbalier onshore tariffs investor relations press releases sec filings events  presentations email alerts faqs ir contact leadership board of directors management team corporate governance careers our culture  overview benefits job search         download most recent investor presentation operations overview since its founding in  energy xxi has become one of the largest operators on the gulf of mexico gom shelf utilizing the latest technologies its existin